---
import Update from "../components/updateComponents/Update.astro";
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";

// css
import "../styles/updates.css";

const title = "Updates";
---

<MainLayout title={title}>
	<div class="updates-list">
		<Update date="November 15, 2024">
			<p>
				Recreated this new web tool (Escalator v2) and made several changes.
				Mostly to make the site easier for me to update
			</p>
			<p>Changed most of the styling in all pages</p>
			<p>Changed the displayed text of all restrictions</p>
			<p>
				The complete detail of each restriction will now be displayed when
				hovered
			</p>
			<p>
				The order of restrictions in escalation is now based on what you click
				(check) first, unlike before that the order is based on how I created
				the site
			</p>
			<p>
				Added clickable buttons in <i>[Device Sharing: First Escalation]</i> and
				<i>[Device Sharing: Previously Escalated]</i> to add account status
			</p>
			<p>
				Some restrictions were updated but I did not include them in the
				changelogs. All restrictions are up to date as of today
			</p>
		</Update>

		<hr />

		<Update date="October 22, 2024">
			<p>
				Added option to add more cards used for larger deposits in SA1
				escalation
			</p>
		</Update>

		<hr />

		<Update date="October 21, 2024">
			<p>Updated "Amount is greater than" escalation</p>
		</Update>

		<hr />

		<Update date="October 10, 2024">
			<p>
				Added shortcut: Press C to copy escalation. (Still won't work if there's
				no escalation checked)
			</p>
			<p>Changed default to "No restrictions/escalations selected."</p>
			<p>Changed background</p>
			<p>Changed header background color</p>
		</Update>

		<hr />

		<Update date="October 8, 2024">
			<p>Disabled fixed footer</p>
			<p>Fixed whitespace not being removed from SA1 inputs</p>
			<p>
				Changed "Amount is more than $5,000" to "Total amount is more than
				$10,000"
			</p>
			<p>Removed "Has 4 or more related users"</p>
			<p>
				Added 4 new escalations based on GeoComply - <a
					href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/11LG_4njZQ9QNBK3g8A37aXZXLqTpZdiR0DE8Zg2EvCQ/edit?gid=1888138481#gid=1888138481&range=A22:B22"
				>
					Device Sharing Decision Table
				</a>
			</p>
		</Update>

		<hr />

		<Update date="October 1, 2024">
			<p>Changed placeholder text for no escalation</p>
			<p>
				Changed cursor to ðŸš« when there's no escalation, indicating that copying
				is not allowed
			</p>
			<p>
				Changed "Copied to clipboard!" pop up location and added a fade-out
				transition
			</p>
		</Update>

		<hr />

		<Update date="September 25, 2024">
			<p>Changed tab icon for all urls</p>
			<p>
				Added 2 new escalations based on <a
					href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/11LG_4njZQ9QNBK3g8A37aXZXLqTpZdiR0DE8Zg2EvCQ/edit?gid=1888138481#gid=1888138481&range=D3:E4"
					>FBG WD Notes Google Sheet</a
				>
			</p>
			<p>
				For name mismatch escalations, number of different names will now
				reflect the count of non-empty inputs (instead of always "2 different
				names")
			</p>
			<p>
				Created another tool: <a href="https://fbgfraud.us.kg/misc"
					>fbgfraud.us.kg/misc</a
				> for my personal use. It's still under development, and I'm planning to
				add more helpful snippets in the future. Feel free to use it if you like
			</p>
		</Update>

		<hr />

		<Update date="September 20, 2024">
			<p>
				Created new domain for escalator: <a href="https://fbgfraud.us.kg/"
					>fbgfraud.us.kg</a
				>. No issues opening the escalator from old link, you'll just be
				redirected to the updated one
			</p>
		</Update>

		<hr />

		<Update date="September 19, 2024">
			<p>Header changes color when there's escalation</p>
			<p>
				Fixed escalation result not updating when clicking outside after pasting
				in an input field
			</p>
			<p>Escalation result will now ignore whitespace from input fields</p>
			<p>Edited footer</p>
		</Update>

		<hr />

		<Update date="September 15, 2024">
			<p>Added updates link for changelogs</p>
			<p>Disabled click to copy when there's no escalations</p>
			<p>Changed "Copied to clipboard" popup background</p>
			<p>Disabled text-select for escalation and selections</p>
		</Update>
	</div>
</MainLayout>
